videos.description: Akim Mitchell drives baseline then makes the reverse layup while looking away from the rim.
videos.headline: Hampton's Mitchell somehow finishes crazy shot

videos.description: Greg Heckstall splits a double-team then finds Charles Wilson-Fisher for the jam.
videos.headline: Hampton is lethal in transition

videos.description: John Guerra knocks down the corner triple and on the next possession, Pablo Rivas hits another 3-pointer from the wing.
videos.headline: NC Central goes on quick 6-0 run to extend lead

videos.description: Malique Trent-Street threads the needle to Trevond Barnes and he throws down the hard slam.
videos.headline: Hampton's Barnes hammers it down

videos.description: Jordan Perkins gets the steal and takes it all the way for the fast break layup to go up by 7 with under a minute to go.
videos.headline: NC Central's Perkins ices conference title
